{"tid":708164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下台灣在港人心中地位已經無十年前咁高","createTime":"2018-06-19T06:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T04:15:14.000Z","uid":189872,"like":15,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"dd529748ff020c8450f8a7c9b5314b09b2db2267","tid":708164,"uid":189872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"十年前台灣娛樂圈堆咩野棒棒堂飛輪海五月天那些年<br />\n今時今日仲有無人會睇台灣藝人?<br />\n<br />\n以前台式料理好多人當高級料理,今時今日全部都食韓國公仔麵,韓式燒烤<br />\n<br />\n台灣人既質素在港人心中都下降中<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係以前夠膽寫篇野話台灣唔好,好多香港人會玻璃心(因為佢地鍾意台灣)話你係五毛"},{"pid":"f7099cc451d45faede417ded37571e16c74498b3","tid":708164,"uid":57835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:44:09.000Z","msg":"最段嗰段你唔講唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37475eb5d9b02b30b06c34e3423c6c7e56f541ce","tid":708164,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"以前香港後生好鐘意台灣既綜藝<br />\n而家台灣流行文化倒退曬"},{"pid":"033faeb3927c1d700e03a396032dc0220fcc875c","tid":708164,"uid":142265,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"台妹地位冇變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9fdb99dc4eaaf9938a6227cac72601c4abf1d7","tid":708164,"uid":189872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37475eb5d9b02b30b06c34e3423c6c7e56f541ce","tid":708164,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"以前香港後生好鐘意台灣既綜藝<br />\n而家台灣流行文化倒退曬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:59:52.000Z","msg":"其實可能無下降,只係香港人轉哂睇韓國綜藝"},{"pid":"a7b449df9c99f75d301ff42183ae01c7063393f5","tid":708164,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e9fdb99dc4eaaf9938a6227cac72601c4abf1d7","tid":708164,"uid":189872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37475eb5d9b02b30b06c34e3423c6c7e56f541ce","tid":708164,"uid":118120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2